node.text:
The Monique Lhuillier Fall 2021 Bridal Collection is regal and timeless with an exuberance for embracing love and life! This season is all about epic volume, bursts of color, intricate prints and unexpected embroideries. The collection radiates joy with fuchsia, feather accents, delicate lily of the valley floral details and exaggerated trains. Romantic with a sense of classic details -- billowing sleeves, softs layers, versatile components such as seamlessly detachable boleros, jackets, and over the top veils complete each look. She's unforgettable.
📸 @j.m._gomez

node.text:
An exuberance of color; Monique Lhuillier Fall 2020 Bridal is a celebration of life. Embracing individualism, this season is all about bold colorful florals, botanical prints, and epic proportions. 
Silhouettes of poetic grandeur with billowing sleeves and exaggerated trains add a modern twist to traditional elements. Versatile components such as seamlessly detachable boleros, capes, and over the top veils complete each look. 
This Bride will leave a lasting impression.
Ready for the Weekend! 🍋🌸🍃 #moniquelhuillier #mlspring22
